def victory_test(parameter)   parameter = "X" or "O"
--------------------------
test for 3 parameter's in a row. Horizontal, Vertical, Down-right diaginal, Down-left diaginal
(put victory test here. Set win to true)

# set victory banner
banner = ''
If win:
  if parameter = "X": 
     banner = 'X win!'
